===Noun===
'''arse bandit''' (''plural'' '''arse bandits''')

#(''derogatory British taboo slang'') A male [[homosexual]].

====Usage notes====
*The term is ued to refer to any gay man, whether or not he actually practises anal sex (as the term suggests).  While it is derogatory when used by heterosexuals, it is also used jokingly by gay men to refer to themselves or each other.